name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Zotero Better-BibTex to Overleaf Local Sync

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sync Zotero Better Bibtex export to Overleaf locally

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Zotero Better-BibTex to Overleaf Local Sync allows you to locally synchronize your Zotero bibliography to Overleaf using the Better BibTex addon.

It will add a new entry "From Better Bibtex" when creating a new file and allows you to update the file from inside the editor.

This extension is open source: https://github.com/vantezzen/zotero-better-bibtex-to-overleaf
